            "title": "「MIAMI QUAY」及「DOUBLE COAST」复活节假期再录4宗成交",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt; 会德丰地产 PARK PENINSULA 两大临海合资现楼项目「MIAMI QUAY」及「DOUBLE COAST」成交越趋炽热,今日共录得4宗成交,包括1宗招标成交,共套现逾3680万港元。<br/><br/>「MIAMI QUAY」至今累售229伙,套现近逾26.7亿港元;「DOUBLE COAST」至今累售399伙,套逾31.4亿港元。 (BC)<br/><br/>#会德丰地产  #MIAMI QUAY #DOUBLE COAST </span>\n</div>",
